Class HomePage

java.lang.Object
objectrepo.HomePage
public class HomePage extends Object
This class represents the Dashboard Page of the application. It contains WebElements for various sections of the dashboard, such as Home, Members, Products, Projects, etc. It provides methods to initialize the page and access the WebElements.
